File: EFF leader Julius Malema has turned former DA leader, Helen Zille down for some tea. JOHANNESBURG - EFF leader Julius Malema has turned down former DA leader, Helen Zille for some tea. Zille extended the invitation to Malema on Twitter for her podcast Tea With Helen for a “for a no-holds-barred discussion on SA's future prospects.” Malema, however, declined the invitation, asking if Zille is lost. The two politicians have previously clashed on social media on issues of race. Guests that have graced her show include Wits vice-chancellor Adam Habib as well as journalists Ferial Haffajee and Max du Preez.